HEADWORD: Gasoscope
<hw>Gas"o*scope</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Gas</ets> +
<ets>-scope</ets>.]</ety> <def>An apparatus for detecting the presence
of any dangerous gas, from a gas leak in a coal mine or a dwelling
house.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

